Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  心都涼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺  你為什麼會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我也一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要保護大家  可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上吧  Operation Start
